text: Giorgi Margvelashvili (; born 4 September 1969) is a Georgian educator and politician. He served as President of Georgia from 17 November 2013 to 16 December 2018.Gelantia, Telara (15 May 2013). Financial declaration of "Georgian Dream" Presidential Candidate .
